{"tid":1258653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油麻地指揮官下令今日（26日）開始不安排前線在伊院警崗當值。","createTime":"2019-06-26T08:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T10:07:19.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5bde36e5cafa76aea649fa4db792c05797589f8a","tid":1258653,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2959281/org/e5b12355d4839082457002b2c2f51204.jpg/YW3Pn3DAWsASCEJhkmgcSmRSuZFroZwzVr-xRFa_sUQ?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2959281%2Forg%2Fe5b12355d4839082457002b2c2f51204.jpg%2FYW3Pn3DAWsASCEJhkmgcSmRSuZFroZwzVr-xRFa_sUQ%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=048134c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《香港01》獲悉，油麻地指揮官下令伊利沙伯醫院的警崗，今日開始不安排前線當值，醫院人員如有需要可致電報案室。廣華醫院則會預留兩名警務人員當值。另外，有消息指，荃灣仁濟醫院警崗也暫停服務。<br />\n<br />\n警員改為坐警車在醫院兜圈巡邏<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原本駐守警崗的警員將會乘搭警車在伊利沙伯醫院周邊巡邏，有需要時會前往醫院協助，而不會長駐警崗。據悉，在醫院周邊巡邏執勤的安排是第一次，相關行動屬上級指示；至於在下午3時許換告示的原因，則是因爲原本的告示字句不夠清晰，而醫院警崗內沒有列印設備，因此需要回警署重印另一版本的告示。"},{"pid":"883feca6247d1f107741dacc6630e088d23c392f","tid":1258653,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQQREDk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQQREDk.png&h=190dd71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2LmYZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2LmYZa.png&h=1855d90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前立法局主席黃宏發踢爆：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">議事規則得撤回 押後 postpone or withdraw</span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇暫緩</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PrrEBU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PrrEBU</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">(懶既直接係最底